Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The brave choice we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Its future is being illuminated♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If we clash our selfish emotions\Nwe can't see it (yet)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫To catch up on the distance\Nwe fled from (see) let's go on a journey♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Even if we can't see the farthest lands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We just burn our lives\Nto keep living in the present♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Proof of the existence we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We kept our voices trembling\Nwhile we brandished it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫No need for regret, we go\Nhand in hand (even the dark past)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We accept it and move forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Instead of choosing an answer shown to us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We're aspiring a new dream (always)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Let's walk along the radiant road♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(#09 What's done is done)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... the whole gang's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might feel out of it\Nfor a while from the sedatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she do, Yamagishi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By applying a sudden high\Nvoltage charge in excess,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she made it impossible\Nto access the hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to recharge it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple but effective,\Noptimal destruction method.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer will it last?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, it was just recharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll last two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two months?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a little longer if you\Ndon't run around everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two months for what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato's time left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y...You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you replace the broken parts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pains me to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but with our knowledge and skills,\Nthere's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato's artificial heart is one of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go take care of that nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say it's fine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never had that long left to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing her won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You don't serve that parfait anymore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina found it humiliating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get a chance to try it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New order in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At it again?\NTakina's going to get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The customer comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the face of LycoReco speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare that you're up for a trip to DA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am not! I was told to come\Nand pick up something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusunoki-san won't take a no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina's worrying about it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Drive any slower, why don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, stupid little punks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look well for someone\Nwho's about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No news gets past you, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to DA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to die, so I'm not doing so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Majima paid you a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you failed to capture him both times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, that's not my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this is the last time I'll be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so aren't there any lighter\Nconversation topics?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what are you giving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have this, Kusunoki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We held onto it to prevent\Nany intelligence leaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I lost it! You dirty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be conducting a large-scale\Noperation to subdue Majima in a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take part in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a very funny joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many have endeavored to turn\Nyou into an outstanding Lycoris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I see you plan on dying\Nwithout fulfilling your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you and I consider to be\Nmy role are very different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done talking. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Takina come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks for giving this back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a thief confessing her crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welco...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parfait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything's fine! But make it fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Fuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'll be leaving right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us an answer by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a reinstatement notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've located Majima's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need more manpower for the raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ain't you the lucky one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh? W-Wait!\N- The operation is in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Leaving already?\N- We'll be taking our leave, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- My parfait...\N- Do come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's her deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she wanted to come back to DA,\Nshe could at least look a little happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did their stupidity rub off on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, we've wrippity-wrapped things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- If you're done, get back here, pronto!\N- Yep. Uh-huh. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you know how busy we...\N- 'Kay, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry for making you have to run...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. What about the ones back there?\NGot it under control?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's fine, it's fine. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Closed)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smoke, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the urge whenever I feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect way to punish yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just quit if you're going to\Nlook so grouchy doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked into it. You should\Nhave asked me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did the almighty Walnut find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to admit defeat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Alan Institute. Shinji Yoshimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but deleted dead ends\Nto be found on them online.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I'd ask someone\Nin the know directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus the poorly-brewed tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika. This is for Chisato's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've realized it, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Silent Jin affair, the woman\Nwho destroyed Chisato's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility that\NYoshimatsu's behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all started 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really was Yoshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure no gun could manage to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a congenital heart defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They give her six months.\NThe disease will kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another product of genius\Nborn of the Alan Institute's support.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A total artificial heart device\Nimplant with no heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several generations ahead of\Ncurrently known technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's the most practical solution\Nto exist yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, it's still not perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a problem with its durability.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid it'll only last\Nuntil she hits adulthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lycoris are in active duty until 18\Nat the longest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's plenty enough if she lives that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty to kill, that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's a talent for killing,\Nit must be delivered to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most essential requirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll meet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you only saw Chisato as\Nan instrument of murder as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did that change?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're watching it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika. Are you good\Nat taking care of children?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're always surrounded by them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job. I wouldn't do it\Nif it wasn't for this bum leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the surgery, I want you to\Nhelp her reach her full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. The DA will take\Nresponsibility and raise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's basically our daughter, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never had an assignment like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't an assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise. Between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I left some\Nunnecessary details there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, understanding his character\Nmight lead us to a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Chisato and I became\Npretend father and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, right? The one\Nwho's saving my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the wrong person.\NI'm an employee here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No one here\Nwears snazzy suits like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:14:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should be thanking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I return the favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been given an important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please carry it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that very purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a savior for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A savior, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a savior as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Savior! Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Savior...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A present? From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it must be a gun to help people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji disappeared after that.\NFrom me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why Chisato doesn't kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why's he after Chisato's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe to eliminate those who\Ndon't carry out their mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't that nurse kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Alan who tried to kill me\Nwas probably Yoshimatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's linked to Majima who\Nprocured those guns that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I know the ideological reason why\Nthey'd give aid to someone like Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we can find out more\Nabout Chisato's heart if we capture Majima?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Mizuki-san as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really have to rat me out, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we can't manage to trace him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the fastest way is through Majima\Nand his glaring movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking part in the DA operation\Ncould be our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to turn them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? I thought you wanted to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato only has two months left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'll return to DA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's even the slightest\Nchance that Chisato can live on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let Chisato know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll tell her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When'd you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the "Yoshi-san" she mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who can say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! He's the Alan Institute\Nagent who gave her aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robota. I've come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Hey, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shut your trap!\N- Hey, welco...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welco...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we roleplaying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Excursion Itinerary)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on a little tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our first stop, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, aren't you cold in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the outfit you picked out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are for summer.\NYou didn't have anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for Chisato-san to pick out\Na winter version for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a diamond in the rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up. Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we haven't found you a coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll run late, so I'll just take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we running\Nall over the place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Temporarily Closed)\NLife never ends up going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Takina! Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Chisato way to\Nroll with the punches!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's biting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Secret.)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going pretty far. Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said you should buy a coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you waiting for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow. Starting at nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd drawn up the perfect schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God's a real fickle one, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped that today of all days,\Nthat wouldn't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you're going back to DA?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! That's awesome! When?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not happy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really would have been\Nperfect if it snowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point worrying about\Nstuff you have no control over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept it and forge onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's usually enough to\Nmake good things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, your plan was a huge success.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had so much fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I need to give DA my answer\Nby the end of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Go on, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it, it's a parting gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'm off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The manga you brought me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The flower you gave me\Nthat I don't know the name of♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You're not here yet today?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.61,0:22:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫I am aware of an emotion never felt before♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Tracing along a picture decorating\Nthe window, I travel through space alone♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫That should have been enough♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If I were to grab your hand♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫This town that knows not of solitude♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Becomes one that I can\Nnever return to ever again♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You reached your hand out to me,\Nand a shadow is born from the light♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Sing for me to listen\Nthe continuation of this story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Take me to a star that I've never seen before♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Call Failed)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yoshi-san".
